+// SPDX-License-Identifier: (GPL-2.0+ OR MIT)
+/*
+ * Copyright (c) 2019 Akash Gajjar <Akash_Gajjar@mentor.com>
+ * Copyright (c) 2019 Pragnesh Patel <Pragnesh_Patel@mentor.com>
